description: With the long days and the hard work, Ty Derrick isn't taking too much interest in the farm life, but when farm hand Elye Black shows him there's more than one way to get down and dirty on the farm, he begins to see the appeal. Ty isn't the first city slicker Elye has had to break in, but he might be the hottest. Either way, Elye takes one look at Ty and decides he's gonna have a good ol' time showing him the ropes, and if he has his way, Ty will get the ride of his life from this ol' farmboy. He may even change his tune about the country way of life. Enjoy!
title: Dirty Farm Hands
